                     <interp inst="t18281204-135-person1171" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker, of High Holborn. I have a watch, pawned on the 5th of November, by a boy, but I do not think it was the prisoner - I gave this duplicate for it.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 11.</p>
